  "text": "Moreover, this analysis was also performed to compare different feature representations in the context of imbalanced learning. Not surprisingly, the mixed representation consisting of many specialized features for sentiment detection such as negated n-grams or polarity values from handcrafted lexicons resulted to be most safe with respect to safe leveles [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Furthermore, the continuous bag-of-words representation resulted to be safer than the classic bag-of-words representation. Nevertheless, all the representations happen to obtain low safety levels which encourages further research in the construction of better, more suitable features representations.",
